<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤ - تَقرِيبُ التَّهْذِيْب. طُبعَ فِي دَارِ المَعْرِفَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥ - تَهْذِيْبُ التَّهْذِيْبُ. طُبعَ فِي دَارِ المَعْرِفَةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦ - ثِقَاتُ الرِّجَالِ مِمَّنْ لَمْ يُذْكَرْ فِي تَهْذِيبِ الْكَمَال.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧ - رِجَالُ السُّنَنِ الْأَرْبَعَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٨ - لِسَانُ الْمِيزَان.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٩ - نُزْهَةُ الْألْبَابِ فِي الْأَلْقَابِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٠ - المُعْجَمُ المُفَهْرَس. طُبِعَ فِي دَارِ المَعْرِفَةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١١ - الْإِصَابَة فِي تَمْيِزِ الضَحَابَة.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٢ - إِنْبَاء العُمْر بِأَنْبَاءِ العُمُر.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١٣ - تَرْجَمَةُ ابْنُ تَيْمِيَةَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٤ - تَرْجَمَةُ النَّوَوِي.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١٥ - الدُرَرُ الكَامِنَة فِي أَعْيَانِ المَائَةِ الثَّامِنَة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٦ - التَّرْجَمَةُ الْغَيْثِيَّةِ بَالتَّرْجَمَةِ اللَّيْثِيَّةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٧ - زَوَائِدُ <span class="c1">"طَبَقَاتُ الشَّافِعِيَّةِ الوُسْطَى"</span> للتاج السبكي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١٨ - السِّيرَةُ النَّبَوِيَّة.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>١٩ - مُخْتَصَرُ الْبِدَايَةِ وَالنِّهَايَةِ لابْنِ كَثِيرِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٢٠ - مُنْتَخَبُ تَارِيْخُ قَبْرولِي.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٢١ - مُنْتَقَي مِنْ تَارِيْخِ ابْنِ خلْدُون.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٢٢ - مُنْتَقَى مِنْ تَارِيْخِ ابْنِ عَسَاكِرِ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٢٣ - نَظْمُ وَفِيَّاتِ الْأعيَانِ للذهبي، وغيرهما كثير.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>